{"id": 3315, "title": "Ticket #3315: tighten the permissions on execute directories", "description": "<blockquote>\ncurrently execute directories are created with permissions 0755.  there's no good reason for them to be world-readable other than condor has relied on that to do various things like monitor disk activity and \"park\" in that directory with chdir.\n\n<p>this work will change the execute dir to be created with permissions 0700, and then change the various other activities condor does to be done with user priv instead of condor priv.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3326\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3326'); return false;\" title='add a \"dirusage\" command to the privsep switchboard'>#3326</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nadd a \"dirusage\" command to the privsep switchboard</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Dec-04 15:10</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/145dace1f138782a24488da4c6b495cba583a236\">[34270]</a></span>: version history item about tightening permissions on execute directory ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3315\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3315'); return false;\" title=\"tighten the permissions on execute directories\">